    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041023005",
    "title": "揺れるマインド",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "次のレースに向けた戦略を練るため、\r\nビワハヤヒデとミーティングをしていたある日のこと。",
            "enText": "One day, I was meeting with Biwa Hayahide to \nplan a strategy for the next race.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -2613422708197467231
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -4471263707672872482
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2483618182754824581,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "――以上の数値から、今回のレースはやや前傾気味に進行すると\r\n予想ができる。さて、ここで今一度出走ウマ娘について確認したい。",
            "enText": "—Based on the above figures, we can expect the race to be run \nwith a slight forward tilt. Now, I would like to check the \nhorses in the race once again.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 328,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 237,
                    "pathId": -3201224104071802880
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -4066994704108408805
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5833621050946300176,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "先ほどキーとなるのは4番の彼女だと伝えたが、\r\n彼女の過去3レースのデータを参照されたい。つまり――",
            "enText": "I told you earlier that the key is her #4, \nand I refer you to the data from her last \nthree races. In other words—",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 257,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 269,
                    "pathId": -7120396010610939110
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 237,
                    "pathId": -9090969053018228367
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5623504109039647196,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "相変わらず彼女の理論は高度で、話を追うのがやっとだ。\r\n置いていかれないよう必死にメモを取っていると……。",
            "enText": "As usual, her theories are so advanced that I can \nbarely follow what she is saying. I was frantically \ntaking notes so as not to be left behind…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 213,
                    "pathId": -8186792014698732213
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": -5757543621613601996
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -599307014001185579,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトA",
            "enName": "Classmate A",
            "jpText": "ねえ、あそこ。\r\nハヤヒデさん、めちゃくちゃ難しそうな話してる。",
            "enText": "Hey, over there. Hayahide-san, you're talking \nabout something really difficult.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 165,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -4947946756850440556
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 194,
                    "pathId": 1315906202543935712
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8267390925235939926,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトB",
            "enName": "Classmate B",
            "jpText": "わ、ホントだ。さすが学年トップクラスの秀才、\r\nやっぱりすごいなぁ～……レベルが違うわ。",
            "enText": "Wow, it's true. As expected of a top \nclass student, she's still amazing～… \nlevel is different.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 281,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 216,
                    "pathId": 9123428827930873724
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 322,
                    "pathId": -268657709692693813
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1054563792445454654,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトA",
            "enName": "Classmate A",
            "jpText": "何してたらあんなに頭よくなるんだろうね。\r\n勉強しまくったらいいのかなぁ？",
            "enText": "I wonder what they do to become so smart. I \nwonder if I should study all the time?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 186,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 143,
                    "pathId": -3981042101813276020
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 322,
                    "pathId": 4525006846144999142
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6986438659085332629,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトB",
            "enName": "Classmate B",
            "jpText": "ああいうヒトは元から頭の出来が違うの！\r\nウチらじゃ無理だって～。",
            "enText": "People like that are not naturally \nsmart! We can't do it!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 201,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 292,
                    "pathId": 8376411293754076524
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": -5019689578533975857
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7674064939654648482,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……『すごい』、か。",
            "enText": "… 'Amazing', huh?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 62,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ハヤヒデ？",
                    "enText": "Hayahide?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 292,
                    "pathId": 232570340865883287
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 5744800255895003268
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8117286007395134217,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "いや……なんでもない。\r\nさて、ミーティングを続けよう。",
            "enText": "No… it's nothing. Now, \nlet's continue the meeting.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 152,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 292,
                    "pathId": 3950049678676971705
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -7346920945926858561
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1141712978060316521,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しかしその後のミーティング中も、\r\nビワハヤヒデは時折考え込む様子を見せ――",
            "enText": "However, during the meeting that followed, \nBiwaHayahide occasionally appeared \nto be lost in thought.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 4462346580912962844
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -3252030972370356109
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1120779606463120769,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……。",
            "enText": "…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 36,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 6935616763578090774
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": 8459905603511804910
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4236441131625393446,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――カフェテリアを出た後も、どこか浮かない表情をしていた。",
            "enText": "-She had a somewhat unflattering expression \non her face after leaving the cafeteria.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……クラスメイトの話が気になってる？",
                    "enText": "… wondering what your classmates \nare talking about?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 8971487679801378462
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3715943433574244991,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……っ。いや……そうだな、すまない。\r\n何、大したことじゃないよ。",
            "enText": "… No… you're right, sorry. \nWhat, it's no big deal.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 231,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺でよければ、話してみてほしい",
                    "enText": "If it's okay with me, I'd \nlike you to talk to her.",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私でよければ、話してみてほしい",
                    "enText": "If it's okay with me, I'd \nlike to talk to you.",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 143,
                    "pathId": 7160414524798958095
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1839196342566269656
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8250452835823773899,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……。",
            "enText": "…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 37,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -6079528487732882715
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 1317519396223584297
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1728932362615646734,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……『すごい』と形容されると、違和感があるんだ。\r\nその単語には、『並外れている』という意味が含まれるだろう。",
            "enText": "I feel uncomfortable when people describe me \nas… 'amazing'. The word would include \nthe meaning 'extraordinary'.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 282,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 255,
                    "pathId": 7269045428694137753
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8053983639727127988
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6994609061517114845,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "確かに傍から見れば、理詰めで事を進めていく私は、\r\n難しいことをしているように見えるかもしれない。だが……。",
            "enText": "Sure, from the outside it may appear that I'm \ndoing the hard thing, trying to reason my \nway through things. But…",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 259,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 273,
                    "pathId": -915790640216687472
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 269,
                    "pathId": 1276196114660665728
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6867507269726706744,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "凡人たる私には、理論武装という道しかなかっただけだ。\r\nでなければ、この学園に入学もできなかっただろう。",
            "enText": "As an ordinary person, I had no choice but to \ntake the theoretical path. Otherwise, I would \nnot have been able to enter this school.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 291,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 275,
                    "pathId": -2524145435444268325
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -7486129328465755641
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3476910069927046008,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "故に本来、『すごい』という言葉は……\r\n天賦の才を持ったウマ娘を指すべきなんだ。",
            "enText": "Therefore, the word 'amazing' should \noriginally refer to… a horse girl with \nnatural talent.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 202,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 1994569415374189403
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -1249635601990177299
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1691660406480608784,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "恐らく彼女が思い描いているのは、\r\n妹――“怪物”ナリタブライアンのことだろう。",
            "enText": "Perhaps she is thinking of her sister, \nthe \"monster\" Naritabryan.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 1299586247515029050
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": 3709705545294863785
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5976514934506864271,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "偉大な妹を持つ彼女には、他人には知れない\r\n複雑な想いがあるのかもしれない。だが――それでも。",
            "enText": "Having a great sister, she may have some \ncomplicated feelings that others may not \nknow. But still.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君の理論は、『すごい』武器だ！",
                    "enText": "Your theory is an 'awesome' weapon!",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方の理論は、『すごい』武器だよ！",
                    "enText": "Your theory is an 'awesome' weapon!",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 159,
                    "pathId": 2413222948039696797
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 163,
                    "pathId": -1014447639123954849
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5340926519617409301,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "努力で自分だけの武器を磨いてきたビワハヤヒデ。\r\nそんな彼女が素晴らしい存在であることは疑うべくもないと伝えた。",
            "enText": "Biwa Hayahide has honed her own unique weapon \nthrough hard work. I told her that there is no \ndoubt that she is such a wonderful person.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 3318945444683242048
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7728704135819482241
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5928460207286151579,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……ありがとう。",
            "enText": "Thanks…",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 8980346198084645640
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 371176111855970208,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "そうだな。私はこの武器に更に磨きをかけ、君と共に\r\nこの厳しい戦いを切り抜けていく。その意志は変わらないよ。",
            "enText": "Yes, I do. I will further hone this weapon, \nand together with you, we will get through \nthis tough battle. I will not change my mind.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 348,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 305,
                    "pathId": -6103666885899571040
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -7073197573543300187
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2401670015165900155,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "だがね、トレーナー君。姉として……\r\nただ優れていたかったと思うのも本心なんだ。",
            "enText": "But you see, Ms. Trainer. I also really wish \nI had just excelled… as a sister.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 282,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 171,
                    "pathId": 7123117756115776289
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 310,
                    "pathId": 8188536735001109831
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": 1079495018617979800
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": -6830764236997762246
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3975458122896307736,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "素質という、努力ではどうにもならない部分さえ\r\n求めるなど、自分でも呆れるがね。",
            "enText": "I am astonished at myself for even asking for \na part that cannot be dealt with by effort, \nnamely, a predisposition.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 252,
                    "pathId": -1273479975508274452
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": -1575009372728592600
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 252,
                    "pathId": 5682285886786219011
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -8289876975914812701
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6174108998369123888,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "遠くを見やるビワハヤヒデからは、ちょっとした自信の無さが\r\n見てとれる。常日頃から冷静な彼女にも、脆い部分はあるのだ。",
            "enText": "Looking into the distance, Biwa Hayahide shows \na slight lack of confidence. She is always calm, \nbut even she has her fragile side.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 171,
                    "pathId": 5428019778294185560
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 211,
                    "pathId": -4369913423158217820
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 246,
                    "pathId": 4804042858518406146
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": -2301782168136995470
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 6488307341016636597
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8189122290874596219,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "いや、つまらない話をしたな。この後は……予定にはないが、\r\n先ほどのミーティングを踏まえトレーニングをしたい。",
            "enText": "No, that was boring talk. After this, I would \nlike to train based on the meeting we just had, \nalthough it is not on the… schedule.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 269,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 261,
                    "pathId": 6359952298137022997
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2983052951975494984
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7136542562375408900,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "式の検証は迅速に。でなければ、\r\n誤っていた場合に立て直すのが遅くなるからな。",
            "enText": "Verify formulas promptly. Otherwise, it will \nbe too late to correct it if it is wrong.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 220,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 4304482534902851543
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": -8874208989798304299
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1926992268608673129,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "何かに追い立てられるように先を行くビワハヤヒデに、\r\nどうすれば自信を持ってもらえるのか考えさせられる出来事だった。",
            "enText": "The event made me think about how to give \nconfidence to Biwa Hayahide, who is pushing \nahead of the pack as if driven by something.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -2165817090181217096
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -180160834477435576
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4675823495615982557,
            "blockIdx": 30
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1669933695
}